{"tid":237374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國無懼火雞　重裝武器支援庫爾族重奪拉卡","createTime":"2017-05-10T10:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T10:49:17.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8d924fedd8fad94aab1e45f069e2f2def22ad2","tid":237374,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"【打擊IS】白宮批准向庫爾德族提供武器 勢得罪土耳其 <br />\n<br />\n 美國不理會北約成員國土耳其反對，將向庫爾德族民兵提供武器，在敍利亞打擊極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部周二表示，總統特朗普周一批准向庫德族部隊提供武器。消息指美國將供應彈藥、小型武器、機關槍、推土機和裝甲車等。<br />\n<br />\n美國支持的「敍利亞民主部隊」（SDF）由庫爾德族和阿拉伯武裝組織組成，美軍提供訓練及擔任顧問，目前與IS爭奪拉卡控制權。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其視庫爾德族武裝為恐怖分子，不願見到他們佔據更多敍利亞領土，故反對美國向庫爾德族武裝提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司／美聯社 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170510/56673577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170510%2F56673577&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IawHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6575de93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170510%2F56673577&h=bec47744\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170510/56673577</a>"},{"pid":"7b4e2244404ad0fbad5ff40656d27f8756648953","tid":237374,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"踢火雞老母出北約啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都準備變返傳統伊斯蘭國家"},{"pid":"138321987256fbc24a3a48e60b20faa44707e532","tid":237374,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踢火雞老母出北約啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都準備變返傳統伊斯蘭國家</blockquote><br />\n難民問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}